<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.2">
<l>neñcamē nīṇaka rāka viruntavaṉ</l>
<l>ṟañcaṉē taṇṇilaṅ kaikkiṟai yaicceṟṟa</l>
<l>nañcaṉē ñālaṅkoḷ vāṉkuṟa ḷākiya</l>
<l>vañcaṉē yeṉṉu meppōtumeṉ vācakamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“My refuge where [my] heart sits while in the tall city,</l>
<l>poisonous one who destroyed the lord of cool Laṅka,</l>
<l>deceiver who became a dwarf in order to take the world”,</l>
<l>[thus] says my speech all the time.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
